<td>
<p>Welcome to Go Newsletter Issue #22. Videos from FOSDEM are now up as one epic playlist, and there are a number of excellent in-depth articles in this issue. Don't forget there's also a <a href="http://twitter.com/golangweekly">Go Newsletter twitter account</a> if you'd like to get more frequent updates. Compiled by <a href="https://twitter.com/mattrco">Matthew Cottingham</a> and <a href="https://twitter.com/kelseyhightower">Kelsey Hightower</a>.</p>
</td>
</tr>
